| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5609 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 169bbae8-fb8d-5fdc-9fc9-1710bd65eff3"
